<div class="teacher-header"><h1>Catree Barrett</h1><div class="sm"><a href="https://twitter.com/siromaniwell" title="Twitter"><svg class="icon icon-twitter"><use xlink:href="#icon-twitter"></use></svg><span>Twitter</span></a></div></div><img src="images/teachers/bio-pages/catri-barrett.jpg" alt="Catri Barrett" class="w350fr"><p>After experiencing profound physical and mental benefits from a regular Yoga practice, Catree decided to travel to India where she completed her 200hr teacher training at Kranti Yoga, Goa.</p><p>Catree&rsquo;s accessible approach incorporates her own personal development, healing and yoga experiences to her teaching, with her main aims being to inspire, support and assist her students in achieving their full potential on and off the mat. Expect to leave Catree&rsquo;s classes feeling calm, energised and balanced.</p>